Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,五年裡  我被困在地獄一般的小島上\N{\b0\fs12}After five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來只有一個目標\N{\b0\fs12}I have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}To save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手\N{\b0\fs12}But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我的朋友  我只能偽裝成另一個人\N{\b0\fs12}To honor my friend's memory, I must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}深切懷念托馬斯•梅林\N孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,成為另一種存在\N{\b0\fs12}I must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃殺了莎朵\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo killed Shado.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我選擇了救你\N{\b0\fs12}Because I chose to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,殺害了莎朵的人還在逍遙法外\N{\b0\fs12}The man who killed Shado is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會逍遙很久的  因為我們要奪下貨船\N{\b0\fs12}Not for long. Because we're going to take the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林才是西婭的親生父親\N{\b0\fs12}Merlyn is Thea's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我認為你應該親口告訴奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}But I thought you deserved to tell Oliver yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不會告訴我兒子任何事情的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not going to tell my son anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭永遠都不能知道梅林的事\N{\b0\fs12}Thea can never find out about Merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,從現在開始  我們再無瓜葛\N{\b0\fs12}As of right now, we have no relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之間再無關係\N{\b0\fs12}You and I are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,親愛的  你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Sweetheart, are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們生活中出現的\N{\b0\fs12}Every single thing that's gone wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所有不愉快都是你的錯\N{\b0\fs12}in our lives is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我滾\N{\b0\fs12}Now get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-對不起  -我讓你滾\N{\b0\fs12}- I'm sorry. - I said, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,六秒後\N{\b0\fs12}In six seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}克羅企業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大廳裡的保安會換班\N{\b0\fs12}lobby security will undergo a shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候  你走到電梯裡去\N{\b0\fs12}When that happens, make for the elevator bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\b0\fs12}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,記住我跟你說的\N{\b0\fs12}Now, remember what I told you--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,時機就是一切\N{\b0\fs12}timing is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,保持每秒1.3秒的速度\N{\b0\fs12}Maintain a pace of 1.3 meters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,六秒走到目標處\N{\b0\fs12}per second. Six seconds to target.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,5  4\N{\b0\fs12}5, 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}克羅企業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在  先生們\N{\b0\fs12}Now is the time, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是指紋識別器  我破解不了\N{\b0\fs12}It's a fingerprint reader. I can't crack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我能\N{\b0\fs12}I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有5.3秒的時間走到東樓梯\N{\b0\fs12}You have 5.3 seconds to get down the east stairwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,別走了\N{\b0\fs12}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們拿到了想要的東西\N{\b0\fs12}We got what we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他說了等等\N{\b0\fs12}He said to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在明處等著嗎  別管了\N{\b0\fs12}Out in the open? Forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣  別這樣\N{\b0\fs12}Don't do it. Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,保安發現了我們\N{\b0\fs12}Security clocked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警局嗎  你們得派點警官過來\N{\b0\fs12}SCPD? You've got to send some officers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,上面  三樓  三樓\N{\b0\fs12}Up there, third floor. Third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他們通知了星城警局\N{\b0\fs12}They've alerted the SCPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,22秒內從東大廳的出口離開\N{\b0\fs12}Exit the east lobby in 22 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,星城警局  放下武器\N{\b0\fs12}SCPD! Put your weapons down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾查克\N{\b0\fs12}Walczak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,DC52向搜查小隊呼叫  市中心需要支援\N{\b0\fs12}Delta Charlie 52 to search, I need back-up, downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,離開這裡  走開\N{\b0\fs12}Get out of here. Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開  讓開\N{\b0\fs12}Move. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一切權力歸人民\N{\b0\fs12}Power to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《綠箭》  第二季第十四集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格\N{\b0\fs12}Dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  對不起\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係  我沒事\N{\b0\fs12}It's ok, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看  讓我看看\N{\b0\fs12}Let me see. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她在流血  但是傷口不深\N{\b0\fs12}She's bleeding, but it's not deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真好  我不能再留疤了\N{\b0\fs12}Good, I can't take any more scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,話說  你這是迫擊炮留下的傷\N{\b0\fs12}Speaking of... mortar round?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  簡易爆炸裝置  在阿富汗的派克迪卡省  眼力不錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, IED, the Paktika province in Afghanistan. Good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,傷口我很熟\N{\b0\fs12}I know my wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,手榴彈  在阿爾及爾\N{\b0\fs12}Grenade. Algiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒被手榴彈炸傷過\N{\b0\fs12}I've never been hit by a grenade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上那麼多傷疤  居然沒被手榴彈炸傷過\N{\b0\fs12}All those scars, you've never been hit by a grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,箭傷  刀傷  刀傷\N{\b0\fs12}Arrow, knife, knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受過很多槍傷  沒有手榴彈\N{\b0\fs12}A lot of bullets, no grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近中彈了\N{\b0\fs12}I've got myself a new bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,九毫米  就在這\N{\b0\fs12}Nine millimeter, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,38毫米口徑  我主要是劍傷  還有一處矛傷\N{\b0\fs12}.38. I'm mostly swords, and a spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一塊傷疤\N{\b0\fs12}I have a scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在我嘴裡\N{\b0\fs12}It's in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,16歲時我拔了智齒\N{\b0\fs12}I had my wisdom teeth removed when I was 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,縫了三針  嵌得很緊\N{\b0\fs12}Three stitches. They were really badly impacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是很可愛\N{\b0\fs12}You're still cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該出發了\N{\b0\fs12}We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,總不能在自己的歡迎派對上遲到\N{\b0\fs12}You don't want to be late for your own welcome home party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒必要給我開派對  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}You didn't have to throw me a party, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  死裡逃生  就得開派對\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, when you come back from the dead, you get a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這是奎恩家的傳統\N{\b0\fs12}It's a Queen family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭斯家的傳統是永遠記仇\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know how well that's going to work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好像咱家傳統也沒什麼用啊\N{\b0\fs12}with the Lance family tradition of holding grudges forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她會想通的\N{\b0\fs12}She'll come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也許吧\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我們該繼續\N{\b0\fs12}And maybe we should keep what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把我倆的事保密\N{\b0\fs12}between you and me between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為了勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}For Laurel's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\b0\fs12}I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我連煉獄島和南達爾巴特都挺過來了\N{\b0\fs12}I survived Lian Yu and Nanda Parbat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一個雞尾酒宴會還是應付得來的\N{\b0\fs12}I guess I can handle a cocktail party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不一定\N{\b0\fs12}That wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不可能做到\N{\b0\fs12}We're never going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃有八名全副武裝的保鏢  隨時待命\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo has eight guards on deck at all times, all armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被看到  就是我們的死期\N{\b0\fs12}The second they see us, we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,首先得處理艾沃的防禦系統\N{\b0\fs12}Assuming we can deal with Ivo's defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼靠近那艘船\N{\b0\fs12}How are we going to get close enough to board the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以造個木筏\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe we build a raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得花幾個星期才能砍到足夠的木材\N{\b0\fs12}It'll take us weeks to find the timber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒那麼多時間\N{\b0\fs12}We don't have weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這座島上待了264天\N{\b0\fs12}I've been on this island for 264 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我有的是時間\N{\b0\fs12}All I have is weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴\N{\b0\fs12}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用維護我  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}You don't have to stick up for me, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼  不是\N{\b0\fs12}What? No,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個都別說話\N{\b0\fs12}both of you shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,聽\N{\b0\fs12}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們聽到了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-在下面  -救命\N{\b0\fs12}- Hey, down here! - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我們坐在監控攝像頭前面\N{\b0\fs12}You left us sitting in front of the security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,保安完全可能殺了我們\N{\b0\fs12}Guards could have killed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你在聽嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你們聽我的\N{\b0\fs12}If you had simply waited
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再靜待五秒鐘\N{\b0\fs12}for five more seconds, like you were told,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒有人會死\N{\b0\fs12}No one would have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我可不會把自己的生命\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry. I wasn't going to bet ten to twenty up in iron heights
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,賭在你那使用碼錶的技能上\N{\b0\fs12}on your skills with a stopwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"所有勇士中最強大的兩個\N{\b0\fs12}"The strongest of all warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是時間與耐心"\N{\b0\fs12}are these two-- time and patience."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,出自《戰爭與和平》\N{\b0\fs12}It's from "War and peace."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,第1440頁\N{\b0\fs12}1,440 pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,書挺厚的  不過很值得閱讀\N{\b0\fs12}It takes a while, but it's worth a read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,托爾斯泰知道耐心是力量的象徵\N{\b0\fs12}Tolstoy knew that patience was the epitome of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,停下腳步需要勇氣\N{\b0\fs12}It takes fortitude to stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在不合時宜的時候行動\N{\b0\fs12}Just as it is a sign of weakness or cowardice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是弱者和懦夫的表現\N{\b0\fs12}to move when you should not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著\N{\b0\fs12}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我們完成了工作  你欠我一個人情\N{\b0\fs12}We did the job. You owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,死後就一了百了\N{\b0\fs12}The dead are owed nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,進來吧  進來進來\N{\b0\fs12}Ah, come in. Come in, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Welcome home, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你能來我真是太開心了  跟我來\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so happy you're here. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  這位是辛\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, Sara, this is Sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你們兩個認識嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Wait, do you two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我們不認識\N{\b0\fs12}Uh, no. Uh, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  我只是很喜歡那些死而復生的人\N{\b0\fs12}Right. I just love when people come back from the dead, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,滿足我的戀僵屍癖\N{\b0\fs12}Juices my zombie fetish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}Um, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\b0\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  我是奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, it's Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能來參加聚會\N{\b0\fs12}I hope you're coming to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}奧利弗\N來電
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說你有點生莎拉的氣\N{\b0\fs12}I heard that you maybe were a little mad at Sara,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而我...\N{\b0\fs12}And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她是你的妹妹  你只有這一個妹妹\N{\b0\fs12}She's your sister, and--and you only get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎  再見\N{\b0\fs12}You know? Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾不來\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel is not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也許她需要時間\N{\b0\fs12}Well, maybe she just needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也需要時間\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I needed time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,當你回來的時候  我...\N{\b0\fs12}When you got back, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你非常嚴厲\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I was pretty harsh on you. Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,蘭斯先生  你  你不需要\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Lance, you--you don't have to--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,當你和莎拉一起上船出來的時候\N{\b0\fs12}When you and Sara went off on your dad's boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你還只是一個孩子  你們兩個都是\N{\b0\fs12}you were just a kid, both of you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,無論她能不能回來...\N{\b0\fs12}And whether she came back, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我太過分了\N{\b0\fs12}I was out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是殺人犯  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}You're not a killer, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-走吧  -走\N{\b0\fs12}- Yeah, - Come on, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我真為你高興  黛娜\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so happy for you, Dinah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗失蹤的那五年\N{\b0\fs12}Those five years that Oliver was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就像  我失去了我身體的一部分\N{\b0\fs12}was...like a piece of me was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白你的感覺\N{\b0\fs12}I know just what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉  -沒關係\N{\b0\fs12}- Oh, excuse me. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你會來\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't think you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我家\N{\b0\fs12}This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想裝作母子情深\N{\b0\fs12}And if you don't want to pretend to be mother and son,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就別在我家辦聚會\N{\b0\fs12}then don't throw parties in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你和奧利之間沒什麼問題吧\N{\b0\fs12}Is everything ok with you and Ollie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎  我仍然難以相信\N{\b0\fs12}You know, I still can't quite believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來不敢想像\N{\b0\fs12}I never really thought
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉會回到我們身邊  昆汀\N{\b0\fs12}Sara would come back to us, Quentin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是蘭斯\N{\b0\fs12}Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上到\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,工作的事\N{\b0\fs12}It's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,貧民區發生了殺人案件  我...\N{\b0\fs12}There's a homicide in the Glades, and I --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\b0\fs12}I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上到\N{\b0\fs12}I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我要打來\N{\b0\fs12}How did you know I was calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為蘭斯警探也接到了電話\N{\b0\fs12}Because detective lance just got the same call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼在每個案發現場都能見到你倆\N{\b0\fs12}What, you guys just show up to every crime scene now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,跟著你來的\N{\b0\fs12}I saw you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,鑒證科剛從一個叫艾迪•沃爾查克的人身上找到了這個\N{\b0\fs12}CSU just pulled this out of a skel I know named Eddie Walczak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒見過這樣的刀\N{\b0\fs12}I've never seen a knife life this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是刀  是個分針\N{\b0\fs12}It's not a knife, it's a minute hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是鐘表上的\N{\b0\fs12}like from a clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,幾年前沃爾查克因非法闖入被我逮捕過\N{\b0\fs12}I popped Walczak f or B&E a few years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今早  他和一個同夥涉嫌一起搶劫殺人案\N{\b0\fs12}This morning, he and an accomplice were involved in a robbery homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他們偷了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What'd they steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼高科技的玩意\N{\b0\fs12}Some high-tech gizmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,科爾德的人管它叫  萬能鑰匙\N{\b0\fs12}Kord rep called it a, um, skeleton key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼  你知道那是什麼嗎\N{\b0\fs12}What? You know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是軍方用於破解地方智能目標密碼\N{\b0\fs12}It was intended as a military tool to aid in code breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而發明的一個解碼器\N{\b0\fs12}on foreign intelligence targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩聯合企業的費利西蒂•斯莫克\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity Smoak works at queen consolidated
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,說企業本來也在研製類似的東西\N{\b0\fs12}and she said they were working on something similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但奧利弗•奎恩停止了計劃\N{\b0\fs12}but Oliver Queen shut it down once he realized
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為意識到了它的作用\N{\b0\fs12}what it could be used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼作用\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,稍加改進  它就可以打開金庫\N{\b0\fs12}It could be modified to open a bank vault,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,任何金庫\N{\b0\fs12}any bank vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沃爾查克可沒那麼高智商\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, listen -- Walczak's small-time on a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我懷疑他甚至都不會用這玩意\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, I doubt he'd even know how to use this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,更不要說能闖進科爾德把它偷出來了\N{\b0\fs12}let alone break into a place like Kord and steal it on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沃爾查克只是個傀儡\N{\b0\fs12}Walczak was just the muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要找的是幕後主使\N{\b0\fs12}We need to find the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雙腳間距拉開\N{\b0\fs12}Plant your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣才站得穩\N{\b0\fs12}Strong foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣出拳才更有力\N{\b0\fs12}Equals stronger punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯\N{\b0\fs12}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是為了防身  我建議你練詠春\N{\b0\fs12}If this is for self defense, I'd recommend wing chun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它的原理是借力打力\N{\b0\fs12}It uses your opponent's strength against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很適合身材嬌小的人群\N{\b0\fs12}So it's ideal for smaller people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,比如我們\N{\b0\fs12}like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你一定照顧得好自己咯\N{\b0\fs12}You seem like you can take care of yourself just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,萬能鑰匙找得怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}Where are we with the skeleton key?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你  怎麼穿成這樣\N{\b0\fs12}And what... are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想...\N{\b0\fs12}I just thought I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,正在將沃爾查克的已知同夥\N{\b0\fs12}I'm cross referencing Walczak's known associates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,和國家安全局解密專家的監視名單做對比\N{\b0\fs12}with decryption experts on the NSA watch list,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是需要時間\N{\b0\fs12}but it's taking some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,問題在於沒時間了\N{\b0\fs12}which we don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,鑰匙不僅是個解密器\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, the key is not just a code breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,落進壞人手裡  它完全就是武器\N{\b0\fs12}in the wrong hands, it's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那個殺掉沃爾查克的人\N{\b0\fs12}whoever killed Walczak,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪到用鐘表零件殺人的人\N{\b0\fs12}in addition to finding creepy uses for clock parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很會掩藏蹤跡\N{\b0\fs12}is very good at covering his tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們很幸運  搜查追蹤\N{\b0\fs12}Lucky for us, uncovering tracks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,正是你的強項\N{\b0\fs12}is what you're very good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,果然壞了\N{\b0\fs12}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他快死了\N{\b0\fs12}He's barely alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還有醫療用品嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you have medical supplies at the fuselage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,應該  不多了\N{\b0\fs12}We have -- we have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快去拿  我應付得了\N{\b0\fs12}Just go. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始後悔給你一把鑰匙了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm really starting to regret giving you a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我沒去參加派對\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sorry I bailed on the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜到了\N{\b0\fs12}Ah, I figured you wouldn't make an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,終於有人理解我了\N{\b0\fs12}Finally, someone understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒厲害到能理解你\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I, uh, I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我理解  莎拉沒告訴我們她還活著\N{\b0\fs12}But I understand how Sara keeping it a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,確實很傷人\N{\b0\fs12}that she was still alive could hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我也傷心\N{\b0\fs12}'Cause it hurt me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼聽起來你要說"但是"了\N{\b0\fs12}I sense a "But" Coming in my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  但是我希望你能原諒此事\N{\b0\fs12}But, yes, but I need you to move past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來個家庭聚餐吧\N{\b0\fs12}A family dinner.
