Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,信號追蹤到了...我們的網絡\N{\b0\fs12}It's leading... back to our network.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,塔克曼盜用了我的入侵線路  這是個陷阱\N{\b0\fs12}Tockman's piggybacking off my hack. It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要入侵我們的網絡\N{\b0\fs12}He--he's trying to break into our network.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是想入侵\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在入侵\N{\b0\fs12}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪兒\N{\b0\fs12}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在家嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你安全嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你感到安全的一個地方\N{\b0\fs12}Somewhere you think you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在一個沒有窗戶來讓人爬進的地方嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Somewhere without windows for anyone to creep through?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能是地下\N{\b0\fs12}Underground, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得沒人能找到你嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You think no one can get to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得藏在安全避風港裡\N{\b0\fs12}You think no one can touch you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒人會碰到你嗎\N{\b0\fs12}in the safety of your hidey hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我可以\N{\b0\fs12}But I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有多槽糕\N{\b0\fs12}How bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,塔克曼用萬能鑰匙\N{\b0\fs12}Tockman used the skeleton key
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,侵入了我們的防火墻\N{\b0\fs12}to penetrate our firewall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,並且重新編碼了我們的安全系統\N{\b0\fs12}And recode our security.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上他讓我們的系統去自毀\N{\b0\fs12}Basically, he told our system to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,結果還成功了\N{\b0\fs12}And it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}漫畫中的超級大惡人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,精彩  同步信號之王\N{\b0\fs12}Bravo, clock king.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉在塔克曼的人可以卷錢而逃之前\N{\b0\fs12}Sara stopped Tockman's men before they could
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,制止了他們\N{\b0\fs12}get away with the cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以塔克曼一定會再幹一票\N{\b0\fs12}So Tockman is going to be looking for another score.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或許我們應該給他創造機會\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe we should give him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能打給沃爾特讓他清算出\N{\b0\fs12}Would you call Walter and have him liquidate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩集團股票裡的五十萬股\N{\b0\fs12}500,000 shares of QC stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,把現金放進我在星城國民銀行的保險庫中\N{\b0\fs12}Put it in cash in my vault at Starling National,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他今晚就做\N{\b0\fs12}and ask him to do it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果塔克曼想再幹一票的話\N{\b0\fs12}If Tockman wants to make another score...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,誰還能比忽然有大把現金的\N{\b0\fs12}Who better to rob than a suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗•奎恩更值得去搶呢\N{\b0\fs12}cash flush Oliver Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那如果他不上當怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}And what if he doesn't take the bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理  八十萬股好了\N{\b0\fs12}That's a good point. Make it 800,000 shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我能做些什麼呢\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,赴約去吃晚餐\N{\b0\fs12}Go to your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家人或許在等著你呢\N{\b0\fs12}Your family's probably waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在勞蕾爾家吃晚餐\N{\b0\fs12}Dinner at Laurel's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事更重要\N{\b0\fs12}This is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這裡無能無力  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}You can't do anything here, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家人也很重要\N{\b0\fs12}Your family's important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該赴約\N{\b0\fs12}You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跟我一塊去嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Will you go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我想讓一家人團聚很久了\N{\b0\fs12}I know I've wanted us all to get together for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只是現在真到了這個地步  我很緊張\N{\b0\fs12}It's just, now that it's actually here, I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,上一次我見到勞蕾爾的時候  並不順利\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, last time I saw Laurel, it...didn't go very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且\N{\b0\fs12}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人作伴的話會很有幫助\N{\b0\fs12}It'd be helpful to not have to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我或許應該待在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}I should probably stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這兒又能幫什麼忙呢\N{\b0\fs12}What is it exactly you think you can do here to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果需要我們就打電話\N{\b0\fs12}Call if you need us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs12}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你的錯  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}You know, it's not your fault, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  你們中還有誰能\N{\b0\fs12}Really? Which one of the rest of you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,提供安全維護\N{\b0\fs12}put up the security safeguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也許如果是莎拉的話\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe if it been Sara,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在就不會一團糟了\N{\b0\fs12}we wouldn't be in this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我們沒有談過這個\N{\b0\fs12}Now, I know we haven't talked about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.21,0:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他們倆在一起你一定很難受吧\N{\b0\fs12}but it must be difficult for you seeing them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是他們倆在一起的問題\N{\b0\fs12}This isn't about them being together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我自己的問題  莎拉可以分析血液\N{\b0\fs12}This is about me. Ok, Sara can analyze blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拳打腳踢  她無所不能\N{\b0\fs12}She can kick ass. She can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一一件我應該做好的事情\N{\b0\fs12}And the one thing I'm supposed to be good at,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也悲劇地搞砸了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm failing at miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,現在既然有了她  還需要我幹什麼呢\N{\b0\fs12}And why do you even need me now that you have her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.07,0:24:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你是無可取代的  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Because you're irreplaceable, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我還有很多事要做\N{\b0\fs12}I have a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  莎拉來了\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, Sara's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.57,0:24:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\b0\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.10,0:24:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver. Well, thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.63,0:24:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,花很漂亮\N{\b0\fs12}These are lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.50,0:24:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.61,0:25:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼不記得你也姓蘭斯呢\N{\b0\fs12}I don't remember your last name being Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.54,0:25:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我也不想毀了你們的家庭聚餐\N{\b0\fs12}Well, yeah, I certainly didn't want to crash your family dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我剛好在路上遇到莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}But then...sara and I ran into each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她邀請我來\N{\b0\fs12}and she mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.07,0:25:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴他爸爸會做最拿手的燴雞塊\N{\b0\fs12}And I told him how dad was making his famous chicken cacciatore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上  抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Actually--excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.83,0:25:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}We're, uh, we're--oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.60,0:25:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  蘭斯先生\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, Mr. Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.28,0:25:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  晚飯只能吃匹薩了  真是抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Um, we're having pizza. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我把晚飯弄砸了\N{\b0\fs12}I had a little incident in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.37,0:25:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果六年都沒過碰烤箱\N{\b0\fs12}I guess that's what happens when you haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.91,0:25:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,搞砸也就不奇怪了\N{\b0\fs12}used an oven in six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.22,0:25:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,來塊兒匹薩吧\N{\b0\fs12}Want to grab a slice?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.28,0:25:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我正要把雞肉塊壘成塔狀\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, when I was pitching a tower of caccitore--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  是燴雞塊塔\N{\b0\fs12}a cacciatore tower, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.62,0:25:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,您還在教書嗎  蘭斯夫人\N{\b0\fs12}Are you still teaching, Mrs. Lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.73,0:25:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  在中央城市大學\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, I am. Greek and medieval history
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,教希臘歷史和中世紀歷史\N{\b0\fs12}at Central City University.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.80,0:25:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你也該考慮遞交辭職信了吧\N{\b0\fs12}You could probably give them notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.34,0:25:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我為什麼要那麼做\N{\b0\fs12}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.63,0:25:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  你要搬回星城了  對嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I mean, you're going to come back to Starling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.57,0:25:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.78,0:25:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒打算搬回星城  昆汀\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not moving back to Starling, Quentin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.05,0:25:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉回來了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, Sara's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.61,0:25:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在那有新的生活\N{\b0\fs12}I have a new life in Central city
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的工作\N{\b0\fs12}and I have a wonderful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,工作在哪兒都有啊\N{\b0\fs12}Well, there's jobs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.20,0:26:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是工作\N{\b0\fs12}More than a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.12,0:26:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我認識了  一個人\N{\b0\fs12}Um...I have... someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.68,0:26:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣  那恭喜你了\N{\b0\fs12}Oh... congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.17,0:26:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其實這挺好的  媽媽\N{\b0\fs12}You know, it's great, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.73,0:26:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該過得快樂些\N{\b0\fs12}You deserve to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.04,0:26:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都應該過得快樂些\N{\b0\fs12}Everybody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.14,0:26:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我這不是真的\N{\b0\fs12}You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你才回來多久  一個禮拜\N{\b0\fs12}You've been back like, what, a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.76,0:26:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們甚至都不否認一下  是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And you're not even denying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.42,0:26:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那麼簡單\N{\b0\fs12}It's...it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.99,0:26:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了  有你怎麼可能簡單\N{\b0\fs12}Of course it is. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.65,0:26:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  拜託了\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.38,0:26:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你的處境也好不到哪去\N{\b0\fs12}Dad, you are no better than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.37,0:26:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的以為\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, what did you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.06,0:26:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽會心甘情願等你的雞塊\N{\b0\fs12}mom was just going to sit around and wait for you for six years
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,六年時間嗎\N{\b0\fs12}to bake her chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.13,0:27:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  別說了\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, Laurel, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.85,0:27:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還是期待她會回心轉意\N{\b0\fs12}And sweep her back off her feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.64,0:27:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你說夠了沒有\N{\b0\fs12}Enough, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.22,0:27:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  你知道嗎  我是夠了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, you know what, it is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.19,0:27:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吃完了就滾出這裡\N{\b0\fs12}Invite yourselves out when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.99,0:27:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我的錢包\N{\b0\fs12}My wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.89,0:27:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs12}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我女兒\N{\b0\fs12}She's my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.15,0:27:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她12歲\N{\b0\fs12}She's 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.99,0:27:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要和她講話\N{\b0\fs12}I need to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.80,0:27:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的對講機壞掉了\N{\b0\fs12}Your radio's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.35,0:27:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她媽媽在她嬰兒時就死了\N{\b0\fs12}Her mother died just after she got out of diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.67,0:27:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,死於癌症\N{\b0\fs12}Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.54,0:27:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我\N{\b0\fs12}And without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.26,0:27:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,連一個照顧她的人都沒有了\N{\b0\fs12}she's not going to have anybody to look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.77,0:27:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\b0\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.09,0:27:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我並不認識你\N{\b0\fs12}I know I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.95,0:28:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不認識我\N{\b0\fs12}And I know you don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.62,0:28:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\b0\fs12}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.23,0:28:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你一定要確保我女兒平安\N{\b0\fs12}please make sure my daughter's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.31,0:28:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\N{\b0\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.06,0:28:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你簡直令人難以置信\N{\b0\fs12}You are unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.97,0:28:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是你告訴我  我需要修復\N{\b0\fs12}You lecture me on how I need to repair my relationship with Sara
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.91,0:28:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我和莎拉之間被你破壞的關係\N{\b0\fs12}when you're the one who messed it up in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.17,0:28:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就因為你倆有一腿\N{\b0\fs12}By screwing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.73,0:28:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而現在你要重蹈覆轍\N{\b0\fs12}And now you're doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.68,0:28:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對  是我的錯\N{\b0\fs12}You're right. This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.87,0:28:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  是你的錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Yeah, yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.77,0:28:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你丟了工作  開始吸毒酗酒\N{\b0\fs12}And is you losing your job, doing drugs and being a drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.97,0:28:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我的錯嗎\N{\b0\fs12}is that my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.19,0:28:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是你家人的錯嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that your family's fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.25,0:28:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還是要歸咎于湯米的死呢\N{\b0\fs12}or are you going to blame Tommy for dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.75,0:28:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Screw you, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.95,0:28:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,自始至終我都是支持你的\N{\b0\fs12}I have stood by you through everything--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.48,0:28:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是你酒駕被罰  丟掉工作\N{\b0\fs12}the DUI, losing your job,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.44,0:28:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,還是你努力想讓我母親被判死刑時  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}and Laurel, I was concerned about your well-being
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.25,0:28:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在為你的身心考慮\N{\b0\fs12}when you were trying to get my mother the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.59,0:28:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  你可真是個正直的人啊\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, you've been a real stand-up kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.71,0:29:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  你以為只有你自己\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, do you think you're the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.13,0:29:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很不好過嗎\N{\b0\fs12}that is having a hard time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.51,0:29:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為只有你一個人有家庭問題嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you think you're the only one with family issues?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.54,0:29:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全...你完全不知道\N{\b0\fs12}You have-- you have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.64,0:29:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我家裡現在發生了什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}what is going on with my family right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.79,0:29:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還站在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}But I am still standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.22,0:29:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而你還在指責除你以外的所有人\N{\b0\fs12}And you are still blaming everybody but yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.89,0:29:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你說夠了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.46,0:29:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.43,0:29:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我夠了\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.72,0:29:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我受指責受夠了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm done taking the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.49,0:29:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也關心夠了\N{\b0\fs12}And I'm done caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.43,0:29:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你去喝一杯吧\N{\b0\fs12}Why don't you go have a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.51,0:29:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉點  去吧\N{\b0\fs12}Get wasted, go...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去威登吧\N{\b0\fs12}Go to Verdant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.85,0:29:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我買單\N{\b0\fs12}I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.40,0:30:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你愛了半生\N{\b0\fs12}I have loved you for half my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.40,0:30:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我追夠你了\N{\b0\fs12}But I'm done running after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.45,0:30:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看見費利西蒂了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Have you seen Felicity?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.42,0:30:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有  等等  怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}No. Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.73,0:30:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我去大貝利漢堡店買了些外賣\N{\b0\fs12}I went to Big Belly to get some take-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.90,0:30:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來的時候  她就不在了\N{\b0\fs12}When I came back, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.84,0:30:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我好幾個小時沒看見她了\N{\b0\fs12}I haven't seen her for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.10,0:30:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,塔克曼上鉤了  就是你讓沃爾特存的那筆錢\N{\b0\fs12}Tockman took the bait. The money you had Walter deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.92,0:30:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我在星城國民銀行讀取他的信號\N{\b0\fs12}I'm reading his signal at Starling National.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.36,0:30:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你怎麼知道的\N{\b0\fs12}Wait...how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.53,0:30:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-因為我就在這裡  -什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- Because I'm here. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.60,0:31:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這兒幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.91,0:31:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我在追蹤塔克曼\N{\b0\fs12}I'm tracking Tockman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他弄壞了我們的電腦  所以我用銀行的電腦\N{\b0\fs12}He fried our computers, so I'm using the bank's
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.90,0:31:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,追蹤萬能鑰匙的信號\N{\b0\fs12}to trace the skeleton key's signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.91,0:31:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那夾克是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}And the jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我很冷\N{\b0\fs12}I was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.98,0:31:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾  把她弄出去\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle, get her out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.66,0:31:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,塔克曼弄壞了銀行的安保系統\N{\b0\fs12}Tockman disabled the bank's security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.94,0:31:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我重新弄好了\N{\b0\fs12}I re-abled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.56,0:31:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在阻截我們的出路\N{\b0\fs12}They're blocking our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.21,0:31:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我去處理他們\N{\b0\fs12}I'll deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.25,0:31:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,塔克曼的信號很強\N{\b0\fs12}Tockman's signal's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.06,0:31:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在這兒  很近\N{\b0\fs12}He's here, he's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.33,0:31:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}Find him, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.27,0:31:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要\N{\b0\fs12}No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.01,0:31:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴你們我的準確位置\N{\b0\fs12}I'll tell you exactly where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.55,0:31:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我無處不在\N{\b0\fs12}I'm everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.95,0:31:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  我正在關注地下\N{\b0\fs12}At the moment, I'm particularly focused on the sub-level.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.61,0:31:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,確切的說  是燃氣管道\N{\b0\fs12}The gas mains, specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.05,0:32:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  他關閉了煤氣排放\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, my god. He shut down the gas main release.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.48,0:32:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這為什麼不好\N{\b0\fs12}And why is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.21,0:32:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,積聚多了會引起爆炸\N{\b0\fs12}The build-up could cause an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.43,0:32:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,會的  會炸毀周圍三個街區\N{\b0\fs12}It will. It'll blow up three square blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.37,0:32:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不會的\N{\b0\fs12}No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.22,0:32:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  塔克曼太過於炫耀了\N{\b0\fs12}Wait. Tockman overplayed his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.76,0:32:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,煤氣管道在全市聯網中  那是我的地盤\N{\b0\fs12}The gas main's in the city's network, that's where I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.24,0:32:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我該理解你的話嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Am I supposed to understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.10,0:32:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他想要炸飛我們\N{\b0\fs12}Ohh. In trying to blow us up,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.16,0:32:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這也給了我一個扳倒他的機會\N{\b0\fs12}he gave me a way to track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.34,0:32:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這我理解\N{\b0\fs12}That I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.48,0:33:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.99,0:33:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\b0\fs12}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.01,0:33:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你都不知道我為什麼要這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}You don't even know why I'm doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.71,0:33:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,錢不是給我的\N{\b0\fs12}The money's not for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.17,0:33:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我做這一切都是為了她\N{\b0\fs12}I'm doing this all for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不對\N{\b0\fs12}Doesn't make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.17,0:33:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,光陰似箭[拉丁文]\N{\b0\fs12}Tempus fugit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.30,0:33:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,光陰似箭\N{\b0\fs12}Time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.56,0:33:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.76,0:33:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他的手機\N{\b0\fs12}His cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.57,0:33:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我給他安裝了\N{\b0\fs12}I uploaded the same virus
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.53,0:33:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他裝在我鑄造廠裡裝備上同樣的病毒\N{\b0\fs12}he used on my gear in the foundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.38,0:34:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒殺死他吧\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't just kill him, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.25,0:34:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只是把他弄昏了\N{\b0\fs12}Just knocked him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.74,0:34:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們做到了  -是你做到了\N{\b0\fs12}- We did it. - You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.83,0:34:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定不想去醫院\N{\b0\fs12}Are you sure you don't want to go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你們就從不去醫院\N{\b0\fs12}You guys never go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,另外  狄格給了我幾片那種阿司匹林\N{\b0\fs12}Besides, Dig gave me some of those aspirins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.01,0:34:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在旋轉嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you spinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.19,0:34:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}止疼藥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.19,0:34:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-阿司匹林  -鹽酸羥考酮\N{\b0\fs12}- Aspirin? - Oxycodone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.56,0:34:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是你那麼勇敢\N{\b0\fs12}I wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.57,0:34:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就不在這裡了  謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}if you hadn't been so brave. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.43,0:34:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\b0\fs12}It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.68,0:34:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想說我為某人擋了一顆子彈\N{\b0\fs12}I've always wanted to say I've taken a bullet for someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.61,0:34:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我可以說了\N{\b0\fs12}and now I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說真的  我該感謝你\N{\b0\fs12}So really I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.38,0:34:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都好了\N{\b0\fs12}All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.10,0:34:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不嚴重  但你依舊會留疤\N{\b0\fs12}Not bad, but you're still going to have a scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己的傷疤\N{\b0\fs12}My own scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.58,0:35:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\b0\fs12}Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.52,0:35:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.97,0:35:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾說你可能感覺有一點...\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle had mentioned that maybe you were feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.04,0:35:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被忽視了\N{\b0\fs12}a little left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.11,0:35:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼  沒有\N{\b0\fs12}What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.13,0:35:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\b0\fs12}I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.77,0:35:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,習慣了做你的女人\N{\b0\fs12}used to being your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.17,0:35:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的那種女人\N{\b0\fs12}I mean, not your girl-girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.93,0:35:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的女人\N{\b0\fs12}Your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.22,0:35:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這是同一個詞\N{\b0\fs12}I know it sounds like the same word,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.36,0:35:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但對我來說含義不同\N{\b0\fs12}but it means something different in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.20,0:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你永遠都是我的女人  費利西蒂\N{\b0\fs12}You will always be my girl, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.46,0:35:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我能再吃一片阿司匹林嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can I have another one of those aspirins?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.77,0:35:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.52,0:36:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘗嘗這個\N{\b0\fs12}Try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.95,0:36:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯吧\N{\b0\fs12}Good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.38,0:36:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很不錯\N{\b0\fs12}It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.25,0:36:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這裡調酒呢\N{\b0\fs12}And what are you doing back here mixing drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.55,0:36:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭雇了我\N{\b0\fs12}Thea hired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.64,0:36:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是新的調酒師了\N{\b0\fs12}I am the new bartender.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.00,0:36:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,上大學的時候我做過調酒師  而且\N{\b0\fs12}I bartended in college, and, uh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.76,0:36:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對於簡歷亮點是國際殺手的人來說\N{\b0\fs12}it's kind of hard to get a job
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.77,0:36:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,找工作好像有點困難\N{\b0\fs12}when international assassin is the highlight of you resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.03,0:36:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你會做得很好的\N{\b0\fs12}You're going to do great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.74,0:36:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}來自西婭的短信: 家裡出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我得回趟家\N{\b0\fs12}I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.02,0:36:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is everything ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.57,0:36:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,希望沒有\N{\b0\fs12}I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.61,0:36:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以放心地走\N{\b0\fs12}You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.26,0:37:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我來這不是要殺她的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not here to kill her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.28,0:37:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我還記得你以前在一家\N{\b0\fs12}I remember you used to bartend
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.53,0:37:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很破的酒吧裡做調酒師\N{\b0\fs12}at that skeevy bar with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.90,0:37:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡地上到處都是花生皮\N{\b0\fs12}peanut shells all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.35,0:37:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,奧博麗薇酒吧\N{\b0\fs12}Oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.63,0:37:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.15,0:37:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是來這喝酒的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm not here for a drink or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.14,0:37:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那你來這幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.46,0:37:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我覺得\N{\b0\fs12}Because I realized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.51,0:37:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像也上了那艘船\N{\b0\fs12}that I went on that boat with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.94,0:37:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而且\N{\b0\fs12}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.13,0:37:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這些年來\N{\b0\fs12}I've been slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.97,0:37:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也慢慢地沉了下去\N{\b0\fs12}drowning for all of these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.86,0:37:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,經歷過各種心碎\N{\b0\fs12}And after every heartbreak or
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.89,0:38:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,挫折  失敗之後\N{\b0\fs12}set-back or loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.73,0:38:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我沉到了黑暗的海底\N{\b0\fs12}I sank deeper into the dark water.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.48,0:38:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但當我見到你時\N{\b0\fs12}And so when I saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.87,0:38:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那麼美麗\N{\b0\fs12}so beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.83,0:38:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼充滿活力\N{\b0\fs12}and so alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.74,0:38:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我才意識到這些我都沒有\N{\b0\fs12}I realized that I'm not those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.88,0:38:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不再有了\N{\b0\fs12}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.54,0:38:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  求你了\N{\b0\fs12}So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.05,0:38:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,求你不要恨我  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}please don't hate me, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.98,0:38:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\b0\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.48,0:38:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  我想死你了\N{\b0\fs12}God. I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.40,0:39:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為什麼事都不能讓你掉眼淚呢\N{\b0\fs12}Didn't think anything could make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.79,0:39:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看來我沒有你想的那麼堅強\N{\b0\fs12}Guess I'm not as tough as you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.48,0:39:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那\N{\b0\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.83,0:39:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你這毀了的煙熏妝是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}why the running mascara?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.27,0:39:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才\N{\b0\fs12}I had--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.84,0:39:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才跟我姐姐見面了\N{\b0\fs12}I just had a moment with my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.43,0:39:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是一次很好的見面\N{\b0\fs12}It was a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.23,0:39:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\b0\fs12}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.62,0:39:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然勞蕾爾是我的姐姐\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, Laurel's my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.39,0:39:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也願意有一個你這樣的妹妹\N{\b0\fs12}I still have room for a little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.14,0:39:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\b0\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.69,0:39:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道如果沒有你我會怎樣\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know what I'd do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.44,0:39:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用知道的\N{\b0\fs12}Well, you won't have to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找羅伊了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm going to go find Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.89,0:39:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我們在比賽時\N2008年5月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.96,0:40:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\b0\fs12}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.74,0:40:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太晚了\N{\b0\fs12}It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.86,0:40:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經死了\N{\b0\fs12}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.81,0:40:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都會死在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}We're all going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.49,0:40:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,像他一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.12,0:40:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不會的\N{\b0\fs12}No, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.95,0:40:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我找到了上貨船的辦法\N{\b0\fs12}I think I found our way on to the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.96,0:40:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,降落傘\N{\b0\fs12}Parachute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.13,0:41:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.07,0:41:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.96,0:41:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.09,0:41:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭給我發短信說家裡出事了\N{\b0\fs12}Thea texted me there was an emergency at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.95,0:41:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒出事  我正在開會\N{\b0\fs12}No emergency. I'm in the middle of a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.10,0:41:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭都沒在家裡\N{\b0\fs12}and Thea's not even here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.99,0:41:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那她為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Well, then why would she...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.58,0:41:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-我真不敢相信她竟然這麼做了  -做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}- I can't believe she would do this. - Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.81,0:41:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她這是強迫我們倆坐下來談談\N{\b0\fs12}She's trying to force us to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.87,0:41:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因為她感覺到了我們之間緊張的氣氛\N{\b0\fs12}because she's sensing the tension between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.62,0:41:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟她說了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}And what did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒說\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.79,0:41:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那是為了保護她\N{\b0\fs12}To protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.57,0:41:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是為了你\N{\b0\fs12}Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.40,0:41:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩夫人  一切都好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Mrs. Queen. Is everything ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.90,0:41:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  謝謝你關心\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.48,0:41:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我兒子來看我了\N{\b0\fs12}Uh, my son just dropped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.37,0:41:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  來見見斯萊德•威爾遜\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, I'd like you to meet Slade Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.24,0:41:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你\N{\b0\fs12}It's a pleasure to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.64,0:41:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,奎恩先生\N{\b0\fs12}Mr. Queen.